      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, finished in Arctic Silver over Black supple leather. This 996.2 iteration features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent borescope inspection confirming zero cylinder bore scoring. The C4S wide-body architecture is complemented by the factory-correct Turbo-spec suspension and 'Big Red' Brembo four-piston monobloc calipers. Every component, from the viscous multi-plate AWD system to the active rear spoiler, operates with factory precision. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
